choiceModel

Class RSUE

  • java.lang.Object
    • choiceModel.RouteChoiceModel
      • choiceModel.RSUET
        • choiceModel.RSUE

  • public class RSUE
extends RSUET
    Although it is not computationally the most efficient, the RSUE is implemented as a special case of the RSUET where the threshold is infinity. This should be theoretically sound, and saves a lot of coding.
